#16605
Devil~
Devil~
A very dark red demon with a forked tail.
~
This appears to be a very powerful Devil. The horns
on top of his head are honed to its sharpest, and the
forked tail snakes out behind him, black at the tip, and
almost appears to scorch the air as it wanders back and
forth. The demon's feet are hooves, and appear quite
strong. He has large, leathery black wings extended out
behind him, as well as sharp claws extending from his
fingers. He appears completely unwholesome.
~
