Brandier~
Brandier~
A small sprite, hovering on translucent wings.
~
This is a rather small fellow, with dark blue eyes, and
very thin wings which flap quick enough that you scarcely
can see them move. He hovers here, a few feet off the ground,
reading from a miniture book, filled with arcane runes. He
appears to be a friendly fellow, at least.
~
