#ROOMS
#16604
ShaTain's Throne Room~
You have enter the Throne Room of the Outcast. All over
the walls are the depictions of his conquests. The west wall
has the conquest over the Kindred, of which he is shown
tearing out a Vampire's throat. On the east wall is the
conquest over the Wyrm, of which he is shown standing
on the corpse of a fellow demon, a blade rising from the
other's chest. On the south wall, there is the conquest over
himself, in which he is fighting a mirror image of himself.
Finally, on the north wall, which his throne is against, it
has a depiction of him fighting alongside, and helping,
werewolves and holy mages.
~
