#16605
Clear Fields~
These fields go on a very long ways. Down, there
are stairs which apparently go down a long way...
North is a small gathering of trees. To the south,
there is a circle of stones. The field itself is rich with
wild grasses and grains. It's completely picture
perfect, except for one spot where the grass is pushed
down. As you look closer, you realize that there is a
small werewolf pup.
~
