#16606
Circle of Trees~
This clearing is surrounded by a huge circle
of trees, the only exit is through a small opening
in the south, where you can see a large field in
the distance. The trees themselves are very
large, and their canopy shades this whole area
in darkness. At the center of the clearing, a small
spirte flutters in the air while chanting arcane
runes from a small book.
~
