#16607
Circle of Stones~
This clearing is surrounded completely by dagger-like
stones, each over 7 feet tall. There is a single opening to
the north from which you can escape to. In the middle
of the clearing there is a pedestal from which rests a book
for you to read. The stones themselves appear to be pulsating
a soft blue color. You wonder why this is.
~
